{"tid":1462415,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔，其實你哋識唔識咩叫正評？","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:53.000Z","uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8613f4dd4eb63483be5295c40e28930955e055b9","tid":1462415,"uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"見到「頜骨全碎毀容 醫生轟謀殺」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1461629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1461629</a> 呢個post成800正評，其實你哋係咪想推post？<br />\n<br />\n睇返「回應會員對本討論區評分系統及對管理團隊的各種查詢」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1424552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1424552</a><br />\n，Admin話「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主題的正負評分對主題的熱門分數並無任何影響</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n有時見到慘劇、令人憤怒嘅新聞，居然有鬼咁多正評（like），確實令人感到奇怪，不如admin出個推post掣，一來<span style=\"color: red;\">方便只係想推post嘅人</span>，二來<span style=\"color: red;\">避免策略post因為正負評造成羊群心態</span>，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n更甚可以參考Facebook嗰套，以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等表情作為進階評分制度，<span style=\"color: red;\">表達返大家真實情感</span>，又好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n@LIHKG"},{"pid":"da85328de3ac6a3a19a74bc913db672739181085","tid":1462415,"uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"721、811<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">1. 追究官警黑合作\n2. 追究警方濫捕、濫暴\n3. 追究疑似內地部隊混入本港\n4. 五大訴求，未忘初衷</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2f92c42b98f21e125d5287894170a3fc11eec67d","tid":1462415,"uid":285523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"推介反送中Portal，將精華post集合起來<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/反送中lihkg-portal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2FIRrY8V1N%2